data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a conveniently located community just minutes from shopping, schools, and major military installations in Colorado Springs, this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem is perfect for families, professionals, or anyone seeking a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.    This home offers ample space with an open and airy layout, making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining guests. The unfinished basement is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch—imagine creating a game room, home theater, or additional living space.    The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast ba,r making it the heart of the home for culinary enthusiasts and family gatherings. You'll find privacy and comfort in the generously sized bedrooms, with the master suite featuring a private ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet.    Enjoy outdoor living in the expansive backyard, perfect for hosting barbecues or relaxing on the patio. The attached two-car garage provides storage space and protects your vehicles from the elements.    Convenience is key, as this home is situated close to shopping centers, schools, and all major military installations in Colorado Springs, making your daily commute a breeze. The community offers parks, walking trails, and a friendly atmosphere, fostering a strong sense of community spirit.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this incredible house your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and see for yourself how this property can enhance your Colorado Springs lifestyle. Your dream home awaits!
